c: 10
v: 87
t: "wa'awhayna 'iilaa musaa wa'akhih harun 'ana atkhdha liqawmikuma bywtana fi \"msr\" takun masakin wmlajy tetsmwn bha, wajealuu buyutakum 'amakin tsllun fiha eind alkhwf, waddu alsalat almafrudat fi awqatha. wbshshir almuminin almtyeyn lilah bialnasr almwzr, walthwab aljazil minh subhanah wteala"